    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个页面发布生命周期的时序图，帮团队理解从草稿到上线的完整流程。核心是要体现安全防火墙和可见性策略这两个关键点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Page Publish Lifecycle",
        "Security_Firewall",
        "policy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我打算分成三个阶段：草稿阶段、调度阶段、已发布阶段。草稿阶段里，published_at 应该是空值对吧？这时候安全防火墙会介入吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Drafting",
        "published_at",
        "nil",
        "Security_Firewall"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，published_at 为 nil 时页面处于草稿态，Security_Firewall 会拦截外部访问。另外草稿阶段要通过 content_page_blocks 来添加内容区块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "published_at",
        "nil",
        "Security_Firewall",
        "content_page_blocks",
        "Add content blocks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，草稿部分我先这样画。接下来是调度阶段——当把 published_at 设为当前时间，页面就进入 scheduled 状态，这时候可以更新隐私设置、布局和 slug，这些变动会触发缓存键更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scheduling",
        "Set published_at",
        "now",
        "scheduled",
        "Update privacy/layout/slug",
        "cached keys",
        "updated_at"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后已发布阶段需要两个判断：published_at 小于等于当前时间才算正式发布；可见性取决于 policy 是否允许，比如 privacy 是 public 或者用户已 authorized。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Published",
        "published_at <= now",
        "Visible if policy allows",
        "privacy public",
        "authorized"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，可见性那里是「policy allows」作为条件，然后分支成 public 或 authorized 两种情况，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "policy allows",
        "privacy public",
        "authorized"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，policy allows 是总条件，满足其一即可可见。整个流程从草稿 nil 到 scheduled 再到 published，安全策略贯穿始终。",
      "elements_involved": [
